# OpsTron — Production Readiness Implementation Plan

## What We Are Building

Transform OpsTron from a blocking monolith into a decoupled, crash-resilient system:

```
BEFORE:  POST /ingest-error → [blocks 8s on LLM] → response
AFTER:   POST /ingest-error → push to Redis queue → 202 in 50ms
                                     ↓
                              ARQ Worker (separate process)
                                     ↓
                              stores result in Redis
                                     ↓
                         GET /rca/{job_id} → result
```

