## How to Run After Implementation

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Redis (if not running as a system service)
redis-server

# Terminal 2 — FastAPI (intake only — validates, queues, returns fast)
cd agent
python main.py

# Terminal 3 — ARQ Worker (RCA engine — separate process)
cd agent
arq worker.WorkerSettings

# Optional: scale workers horizontally (run on separate machines or processes)
arq worker.WorkerSettings  # Worker 2
arq worker.WorkerSettings  # Worker 3
```

> [!TIP]
> Workers can be scaled independently of FastAPI. Add more workers to increase RCA throughput — they all pull from the same Redis queue.

